data.description: This beautiful Albuquerque home is spacious featuring a large master suite upstairs, with walk in closet and separate walk-in shower and tub. Out the sliding master suite door is a balcony to enjoy your morning coffee or evening skies.  Upstairs loft features a window seat. The loft area could be used as an office or game room or even extra sleeping area for guests.  Out the kitchen slider is a back patio partially covered by upstairs balcony. The backyard features a manicured lawn, a small water fountain, Gogi berry bush, and plenty of shade from the large tree and a storage shed sufficient to keep your lawn tools. The family room features a wet bar for your entertainment needs and large kitchen island. The list goes on and on.  Don't miss out on this opportunity in a gated community!
